"url_meta":{"origin":35558,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s daily instruction for Fatimah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to Fatimah, \u201cI instruct you to say in the morning and evening: O Living, O Sustainer, by Your mercy I seek deliverance. Take care of all my affairs and do not leave me to the care of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34317,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/20\/muawwidhatayn-best-two-surahs\/","url_meta":{"origin":35558,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mu&#8217;awwidhatayn: Best two chapters for seeking refuge in Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn \u2018Abis al-Juhani reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cO Ibn \u2018Abis, shall I not tell you about the best way to seek refuge for those who seek it?\u201d He said, \u201cOf course, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThese two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22096,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/27\/rahmah-sheep-slaughter\/","url_meta":{"origin":35558,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: Have mercy on the sheep, do not slaughter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Qurra ibn Iyas reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I would have slaughtered a sheep but I had mercy on it.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you had mercy on the sheep, Allah will have mercy on you twice.\u201d Source: al-Adab\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42693,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/07\/allah-merciful-animals\/","url_meta":{"origin":35558,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: Allah rewards compassion to animals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019qil ibn Yasar reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I had taken the goat to slaughter it, but I had mercy on it.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you had mercy on it, Allah will have mercy on you.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 10557\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4962,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/muhammad-mercy-guide\/","url_meta":{"origin":35558,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: O people, I am mercy and guidance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salih reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would address the people, saying, \u201cO people, I am only a mercy and an offering of guidance.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304\u00a015 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0635\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u062d\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064f \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32706,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/all-cures-but-aging\/","url_meta":{"origin":35558,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah placed cures for all diseases, except aging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Sharik reported: A bedouin said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not seek treatment?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYes, O servants of Allah, seek treatment. Verily, Allah did not place a disease but that he also placed its treatment or cure, except for one ailment.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_l